{% set title = 'LTO Network - Use case - ScanTrust' %}
{% set description = 'The revival of the QR-Code with Blockchain' %}

{% extends "base.njk" %}



{% block content %}

<div class="section-container">
  <section class="hero is-medium" style="background-image: url('/assets/hero/hero-uc-scantrust.png');">
    <div class="hero-body">
      <div class="container">
          <div class=""><span class="tag is-rounded is-medium blue-grey"> INTEGRATOR </span></div>
        <h1 class="primary-text">The revival of the QR-Code with Blockchain</h1>
          <h2 class="dark-indigo">Enabling brands with smart packaging solutions for product authentication, supply chain traceability and consumer engagement on blockchain.</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-top">
  <section class="section secondary no-padding">
    <div class="promo-numbers c use-cases">
      <div class="container use-cases">
        <div class="item use-cases">
            <img class="promo-client" src="/assets/use-cases/scantrust@2x.png">
        </div>
        <div class="item use-cases">
            <p class="promo-head use-cases">Involved parties</p>
          <p class="promo-desc use-cases muted">ScanTrust delivers their smart QR-code services to the world’s largest companies, such as ExxonMobil, Unilever, Shell and AB InBev.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutin-top-alt cutout-bottom">
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
      <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">Business challenges</h2>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column card">
          <img class="card-image clip-a" src="/assets/polygons - 1.png">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3 class="accent-text">Data importance</h3>
            <div class="card-description">
              <p>Environmental data is an important source of information for social domains such as policy, legislation, taxation and investments. After all, the data is used to identify trends, to uncover connections and to demonstrate patterns.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="column card">
          <img class="card-image clip-b" src="/assets/polygons - 1.png">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3 class="accent-text">Data vulnerability</h3>
            <div class="card-description">
              <p>The important role of the data from these types of measurements makes them vulnerable to influence by parties with an interest in the developments within such a social domain.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="column card">
          <img class="card-image clip-a" src="/assets/polygons - 1.png">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3 class="accent-text">Digitization</h3>
            <div class="card-description">
              <p>Digitisation is key to drive the sustainability transformation forward. Data insights, combined and mined creatively, help us better understand our true impact, identify the most effective levers for change, and are also key to enabling circular solutions at scale.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container">
  <section class="section secondary">
    <div class="container">
<h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">Integrator overview</h2>
      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40 inverted-mobile">
          <div class="column is-half">
          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">The problem</h3>
            <p class="muted">Every supply chain, regardless of industry, has common pain points that plague the entire system such as volatility of demand, talent shortage, and rising commodity prices. Unfortunately, these issues don't have simple answers and will likely always require constant vigilance due to the inherent nature of supply chains.</p>
            <p class="muted">There are other often more problematic pain points supply chains face such as little-to-no transparency, low quality data, and the ever-present danger of counterfeits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px;width:280px;height:250px;background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/150x150?text=LivIcon')">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
            <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px;width:280px;height:250px;background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/150x150?text=LivIcon')">
            </div>
          <div class="column is-half">
        <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Solution</h3>
          <p class="muted">Enhancing product transparency and increase consumer trust using ScanTrust's Blockchain connectors. Key product information can be made public on the blockchain and once stored, data cannot be altered or deleted.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
        <div class="btn-container has-text-centered has-margin-top-40">
        <a src="#" class="button is-primary">Book a demo</a>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutin-top-alt cutout-bottom">
    <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">Advantages using LTO Network</h2>
      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
        <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter" style="left:48px;height:250px;background-image: url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:26px;top:90px;left:-40px" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:70px;top:20px;left:-20px" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg">
        </div>
        <div class="column is-two-thirds">
          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Lorem ipsum</h3>
          <p class="muted">LTO Network is a fully decentralized and highly efficient blockchain infrastructure that is easy to integrate in existing systems that brings efficiency and is production-ready. Blockchain ensures data integrity and immutability following from the devices.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
        <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter" style="left:48px;height:250px;background-image: url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:26px;top:90px;left:-40px" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:70px;top:20px;left:-20px" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg">
        </div>
        <div class="column is-two-thirds">
          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Lorem ipsum</h3>
          <p class="muted">Where LTO Network focuses on the underlying data security structures, V-ID is a practical platform, intended for direct application in daily work processes. Both companies, however, have the main objective of facilitating the widest possible application of blockchain techniques with the lowest possible threshold for adoption of this technology.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
        <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter" style="left:48px;height:250px;background-image: url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:26px;top:90px;left:-40px" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:70px;top:20px;left:-20px" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg">
        </div>
        <div class="column is-two-thirds">
          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Lorem ipsum</h3>
          <p class="muted">By creating the “internet of environment” (IoE) for rental properties, LTO Network and partners aim to support a letting agency to provide better services to their tenants and to make better, more sustainable decisions in managing their properties.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
        
    <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
        <div class="column">
<table class="table advantages">
<thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">Theme</th>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">LTO Network solution</th>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">Traditional solution</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>

      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Immutability</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">Anchoring (data related to) smart QR codes allows for utmost trust in the sender and the provenance data.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">Smart QR-codes can be linked to a piece of information that hasn’t been properly validated.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Supply chains</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">Using LTO Network’s decentralized workflows, data behind the QR codes can be efficiently exchanged over stakeholder systems.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">Data captured in the Smart-QR code needs to be re-entered at every stakeholder in the supply chain.</td>
        </tr>


        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Costs / Speed of anchoring</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">LTO’s blockchain is optimized for anchoring, making transactions near-instant and affordable.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">Traditional blockchains tend to be very slow and expensive to anchor this many transactions.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
        </tr>
      </tbody>

    </table>
</div>
</div>


    <div class="btn-container has-text-centered has-margin-top-40">
    <a href="#" class="button is-primary">
      Book a demo
    </a>
</div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>

<div class="section-container cutout-bottom-alt">
  <section class="section alt p-top-l">
<div class="container">
        <div class="columns is-centered">
            <div class="column is-three-fifths has-text-centered video">
                <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Zs17a4cDcU4?controls=0" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
